description:
"I do not believe in one single strategy for executing trades. Markets are places where information converges into a single bit of information: price. My trading strategy centers around balancing the main components of what makes up a price in the crypto space:

- Short-term news cycles
- Recent price action
- Historical price action

Because I am very tapped in"" to the pulse of crypto, and Ethereum especially, this gives me an informational advantage over my position and trades. While the information is available to everyone, I think I am uniquely positioned to interpret and digest information in ways that others do not."
name: Stacking Gwei Set II
